AMYS CANDY tracked the leaders from the four path to the turn but was not a factor. SUNNY AND CLEAR saved ground while racing in the middle of the pack but didn't make a serious bid. NIKLAUSIA raced in the middle of the pack to the turn and dropped back. BEAUCLAIRE lost her rider behind the gate and was not a threat.
